snippet.title: Top Gun - Hornet's Nest - C1 M1 - Defend Cruisers
snippet.description: Just an upload of the first mission from Top Gun - Hornet's Nest. I'm probably not going to upload anymore missions, but if I do, I'll go back and upload the movies. What I really want to do is upload Top Gun: Fire At Will, but one of the two installation CDs is broken :(
